    "long_instructions": "### Ramona's Song\r\nRamona is in a groove and really wants to use the Reggaeton Beat and the Groovy Beat 2 throughout his song. She wants you to add bass, leads, and effects to make her song come to life. \r\n\r\nWhen you're finished, your song should sound like: \r\n- The \"Reggaeton Beat\" and the \"Groovy Beat 2\" play together for at least 20 measures.\r\n- Your song has beats, bass, leads, and effects\r\n  - Think about how you can use rests for some of these sounds!\r\n\r\nBe creative! What can you come up with?",
